## 3.1. Noname Pipeline #5700629259435071776<span id="pipeline-5700629259435071776"/>

<a href="data:application/json;base64," target="_blank" download="Noname Pipeline-5700629259435071776.json">Download Meta File</a>

### 3.1.1. Definition
```ts
Pipeline.id('5700629259435071776')
	.name('Noname Pipeline')
	.triggerBy('system_rule_result').when('INSERT-OR-MERGE')
	.enabled(true)
	.createdAt('2021-07-14 21:52:43').lastModifiedAt('2021-08-07T11:30:30')
	// Stage #1
	.stage('aggregate-test')
		// Unit #1.1
		.unit('factor rule')
			.onCondition(Criteria
				.and(expect(byTopic('system_rule_result.factorId')).isNotEmpty()))
			// Action #1.1.1
			.insertOrMergeRow()
				.to(byTopic('rule_aggregate')
					.factor('count').useCount().from(byTopic('system_rule_result.topicId'))
					.factor('ruleCode').from(byTopic('system_rule_result.ruleCode'))
					.factor('topicId').from(byTopic('system_rule_result.topicId'))
					.factor('factorId').from(byTopic('system_rule_result.factorId')))
				.on(Criteria
					.and(expect(byTopic('system_rule_result.factorId')).equals(byTopic('rule_aggregate.factorId')))
					.and(expect(byTopic('system_rule_result.topicId')).equals(byTopic('rule_aggregate.topicId')))
					.and(expect(byTopic('system_rule_result.ruleCode')).equals(byTopic('rule_aggregate.ruleCode'))))
			.end()
		.end()
		// Unit #1.2
		.unit('topic rule')
			.onCondition(Criteria
				.and(expect(byTopic('system_rule_result.factorId')).isEmpty()))
			// Action #1.2.1
			.insertOrMergeRow()
				.to(byTopic('rule_aggregate')
					.factor('count').useCount().from(byTopic('system_rule_result.topicId'))
					.factor('ruleCode').from(byTopic('system_rule_result.ruleCode'))
					.factor('topicId').from(byTopic('system_rule_result.topicId')))
				.on(Criteria
					.and(expect(byTopic('system_rule_result.topicId')).equals(byTopic('rule_aggregate.topicId')))
					.and(expect(byTopic('system_rule_result.ruleCode')).equals(byTopic('rule_aggregate.ruleCode'))))
			.end()
		.end()
	.end()
```
